[{"question":"Who walks away with the gold guy?","answer":"I don\u0027t care what makes you so curious (ph).","docId":"130222pmt","qSentId":15,"aSentId":16},{"question":"What\u0027s the significance of Pistorius getting bail at this stage, do you think?","answer":"You know, I don\u0027t think it surprised the legal experts.","docId":"130222pmt","qSentId":33,"aSentId":34},{"question":"Should we read anything into that or is that a consistent thing in South African law?","answer":"It\u0027s not.","docId":"130222pmt","qSentId":45,"aSentId":46},{"question":"Is that the sense you\u0027re getting among South Africans?","answer":"It is.","docId":"130222pmt","qSentId":58,"aSentId":59},{"question":"Do you have absolute confidence that Oscar is telling the truth?","answer":"No, like I said before, the onus is on Oscar.","docId":"130222pmt","qSentId":87,"aSentId":88},{"question":"What is that?","answer":"It\u0027s basically used to fight the means of fatigue and tiredness.","docId":"130222pmt","qSentId":96,"aSentId":97},{"question":"What can you tell me about Oscar and alcohol?","answer":"Look, that\u0027s the magistrate\u0027s decision and what the magistrate wants during this bail, after this bail application.","docId":"130222pmt","qSentId":108,"aSentId":109},{"question":"He does drink alcohol then?","answer":"I\u0027m sure when he goes out and goes for dinner with his friends and family, we\u0027ll have an occasional drink, but he\u0027s not an alcoholic if that\u0027s what you\u0027re asking.","docId":"130222pmt","qSentId":115,"aSentId":116},{"question":"Are you ready for the next stage?","answer":"We don\u0027t know.","docId":"130222pmt","qSentId":121,"aSentId":122},{"question":"What are your concerns?","answer":"I have to read the conditions.","docId":"130222pmt","qSentId":127,"aSentId":128},{"question":"Would you say the reality is he would have alcohol just not to access?","answer":"Look, I mean, that\u0027s obviously something he would do in his private time or he\u0027s off time.","docId":"130222pmt","qSentId":133,"aSentId":134},{"question":"Have you reached out to him or any of his family?","answer":"Briefly, I spoke to his brother, I called, just to send my wishes and that my thoughts are with him and his family as they are going through a hard time.","docId":"130222pmt","qSentId":145,"aSentId":146},{"question":"And if you did, what did you make of him?","answer":"Piers, I didn\u0027t know him intimately.","docId":"130222pmt","qSentId":168,"aSentId":169},{"question":"Had Reeva given you any indication of any problems with Oscar at all in the whole time that you knew she was seeing him?","answer":"I tried to keep my discussions with Reeva on a business level.","docId":"130222pmt","qSentId":173,"aSentId":174},{"question":"How big could she have become do you think?","answer":"She was on the brink of explosion.","docId":"130222pmt","qSentId":178,"aSentId":179},{"question":"Why don\u0027t you believe him?","answer":"Well, Piers, I think the magistrate raised substantial questions today.","docId":"130222pmt","qSentId":209,"aSentId":210},{"question":"Alan Dershowitz, your response to that?","answer":"Well, there are holes in his story and if the holes are validated by the empirical evidence, by the forensic evidence, he\u0027ll be convicted.","docId":"130222pmt","qSentId":217,"aSentId":218},{"question":"Without that, is it fair to convict him?","answer":"Absolutely, because motive is not necessary to prove.","docId":"130222pmt","qSentId":232,"aSentId":233},{"question":"Alan, we left viewers in a cliffhanger there, you were accused of going backwards, backtracking, what was your response to Gloria?","answer":"I don\u0027t even know how to go backwards.","docId":"130222pmt","qSentId":292,"aSentId":293},{"question":"Why did he have to fire four shots?","answer":"That\u0027s like apples and oranges.","docId":"130222pmt","qSentId":312,"aSentId":313},{"question":"Why not just one shot?","answer":"The four shots thing I find a bit of a misnomer in terms of an argument against Pistorius, if he genuinely thought it was an intruder who is about to attack him, or fear for his life, you look at the number of cases in America where there are states for stand your ground.","docId":"130222pmt","qSentId":314,"aSentId":315},{"question":"Why didn\u0027t he see if his girlfriend was OK and help her to run out the door?","answer":"What are you saying, Gloria, it\u0027s based on calm, rational thought.","docId":"130222pmt","qSentId":318,"aSentId":319},{"question":"Isn\u0027t the reality in the heat of the moment, nobody knows how someone is going to behave?","answer":"That\u0027s right.","docId":"130222pmt","qSentId":321,"aSentId":322},{"question":"Is it a lot more volatile than we may imagine?","answer":"I don\u0027t think the public image is misleading.","docId":"130222pmt","qSentId":364,"aSentId":365},{"question":"Does he like them to the point of obsession, I mean, how would you describe his relationship with guns?","answer":"I think he was obsessed with his own safety and his own vulnerability.","docId":"130222pmt","qSentId":378,"aSentId":379},{"question":"Did you get the sense that occasionally he would drink a lot?","answer":"When I was with him, it was in the lead-up to the Olympics, to the London Olympics, and I think he had some wine around the house, but he very specifically told me he wasn\u0027t drinking at that time in those months, because he said I train so hard, alcohol has the impact of diminishing your training a little bit, and why should I give up anything, even for a glass of wine, because I am working so hard to be as fit as I can be.","docId":"130222pmt","qSentId":402,"aSentId":403},{"question":"And in terms of his behavior around women, did you see anything untoward in that regard?","answer":"I didn\u0027t.","docId":"130222pmt","qSentId":404,"aSentId":405},{"question":"What do you think of skewing it towards a more musical performance?","answer":"I hear the length is quite long.","docId":"130222pmt","qSentId":447,"aSentId":448},{"question":"Ben, the musical stuff is fine, but if you\u0027re skewing it to a younger demographic audience, is it sensible?","answer":"They are balancing it with having the cast of \"The Avengers\" present, Daniel Radcliffe will be presenting, as well as there\u0027s a tribute to the 50th anniversary of James Bond.","docId":"130222pmt","qSentId":455,"aSentId":456},{"question":"But do you see any surprises there?","answer":"Not at all.","docId":"130222pmt","qSentId":465,"aSentId":466},{"question":"Another mention for Quvenzhane, the young girl?","answer":"My favorite film of the year.","docId":"130222pmt","qSentId":515,"aSentId":516},{"question":"Are we all agreed?","answer":"Short answer, no.","docId":"130222pmt","qSentId":549,"aSentId":550},{"question":"Where\u0027s your money, then?","answer":"I can\u0027t bet against Steven Spielberg.","docId":"130222pmt","qSentId":576,"aSentId":577}]